title: Ted Greene - Rare FULL Seminar - 6/6/1993

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/71.0.3578.44 Safari/537.36

description:
A few clips of this legendary seminar have been floating around the internet for a while, but only the first 50 minutes or so have been available thus far. I tracked down the full clinic and wanted to make it available to everybody, so I hope you enjoy! 

Ted Greene is a huge inspiration to guitarists of all kinds. It's wonderful to watch him extemporize about music. This is from an old set of VHS tapes so there is some audio drift toward the second half.

#tedgreene #musictheory #guitar
